{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0b47f40d46","title":"周恩来陈伯达接见福建革造会联络站负责人讲话","origin":"1967年9月9日红代会清华井冈山一部第三动态组编《动态》第145期","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"85a338e3ee","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"0b47f40d46"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4d9a2ea656","name":"陈再道","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"a78a12dec9","name":"福建文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bba079b09a","type":"title","text":"周恩来陈伯达接见福建革造会联络站负责人讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"4e84dfc37e","type":"authors","text":"周恩来陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"ca680f61c6","type":"appellation","text":"〖摘要〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"0dff9209d5","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"f69f74fb8d","type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊！同志啊！你们眼光太短了，什么矛盾很大，哪里有与蒋介石矛盾大？蒋介石打过来你们连自己家乡也保不住，还能够安心这样搞文化大革命？！现在矛盾的主要方面在革造会！不在军区，知道吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"dbbebb168d","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉出了个陈再道，全国就到处揪陈再道，这是对我们伟大军队的污蔑！革造会要听中央的话，要拥护那个八条。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"15b28fe6da","type":"paragraph","text":"你们要顾全大局不要动摇军队不要自毁长城，现在已经到了不能容忍的时候了，今天毛主席批发了九五命令，说今后再夺枪就是反革命行动了。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"443361e9d4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理指示说：你们有两个任务：一要有敌情观念，共同对敌；第二要团结大多数，搞好革命三结合，进行大批判。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"28efeb9cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"会后总理、伯达接见绍安代表。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"},{"id":"a46593b592","type":"paragraph","text":"临走时，对绍安代表说，你们回去后不要搞分裂，要坚持大联合大批判！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46"}],"page":{"id":"cf3fa1fe62","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b47f40d46","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}